  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>띠지 생산은</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-720af2b4-7b3c-4d5a-b8ed-68c9535d71d6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:816px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223965416452/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2a63db5f-52db-43c7-b3f0-b6d3aa0b2860\" style=\"color:#555555;\">추석 선물세트에 어울리는 띠지를 디자인에서 인쇄까지 제공해 드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f374f05c-e09b-4e69-9f0d-46acf4ad23a4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-81248a80-7320-4dd2-baa1-86d6cc703232\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-97f14e54-f8d4-4369-a87d-f279dc027144\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b6f11e08-f02b-45eb-979c-ab3ef2d8cd8b\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>띠지 디자인 : 기본 5만원에서 부터 시작~</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-798d3912-4422-4952-9211-9075f74b460f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-853f8c74-71d0-4955-82e8-08490787efb6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dfae4d1c-5aac-4929-98d5-6b9526ff9bc4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-94126fc0-66bc-4a21-b214-f8b7146c9ce3\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>띠지 인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-35096278-caaa-4dc5-91a1-724a7ac33b37\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3afc1b2b-93c7-4bd0-ad52-f1147ecf89b3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">띠지는 여러 가지 종이로 제작될 수 있습니다. 일반적인 아트/스노우지에서 부터 수입지까지 다양합니다. 물론 수량에 따라 종이 비용의 차이가 결정되겠지만 기본 100개의 경우 종이 비용 차이가 얼마 나지 않을 수 있어 랑데뷰나 반누브지 등 다양한 종이로 제작되기도 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e46a955f-57ef-419e-9370-1cbd80d9f1dc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-db6895cb-8a28-4b87-8505-e934491c48c0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8446945f-071f-48bc-84cb-c47f0155cf39\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-24666f95-0442-436e-854b-2a2072146e9f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사이즈가 80*700mm의 띠지의 경우 46 2절 한판에 6장이 조판되어 제작될 수 있습니다. 그러므로 46 2절 한장에 6장이 제작됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-444671a5-13d3-4f8b-bc92-05437932fc9d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dbbbfa83-1e1e-457c-9821-7a31b8247970\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8544afd6-808e-40be-86bf-bd46ae011b97\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-56811453-0bd0-4e0c-898c-2a68a3dde7bc\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>띠지 인쇄 : 기본 100개 10만원에서 부터 시작~</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d21d17d4-9f28-4041-aa03-e05bba42c524\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:556px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223965416452/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ff5da0d2-8106-4cb6-99d5-51a2e2fcae0d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8f079a6b-38f7-4fbd-b7ba-079c1b9edd5c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2fc56368-b1b2-4fb5-8dcb-e5d5f74c8b0f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 이미지는 46 2절에 7개 조판이 된 모양입니다. 그러므로 46 2절을 15장 인쇄하면 띠지 100개 정도가 인쇄되어 나옵니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-11c603e4-d86b-43f5-9741-1e015baea7c6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7cb6df5e-c880-4bc2-a01d-23ef5f556a0e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-b6e71775-7363-4433-b956-803d3a733657\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6e8caa0c-3989-4da7-8546-6220eecfd1a4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-ebc1d262-4011-470a-820d-7af0cb2acadf\" style=\"\">띠지 제작사양</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d247da5a-db9a-4a0f-82f6-a0122eaf0d26\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-23aa5114-4eb2-425b-a713-acff2aa88bd9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-46a7deb5-ef79-4081-9fd5-9c9617d6b504\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>디자인</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c317bfba-caed-4d53-9f94-55fe6c842044\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-050ff0c4-ce3f-4434-8215-9051697f142e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>상담 후 견적 가능 :  </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-41c4393b-94f0-48d3-a35a-faa462424a6a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디자인은 무형의 영역이라 가격이 천차만별입니다. 반드시 상담 후 견적과 기간을 정하고 있으니 참고하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-29aa53c2-b0fd-4a33-841c-3fddce6570d1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:816px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223965416452/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-87c7012c-b373-4104-933e-a1c6143f370d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-40fffb3f-dba4-4102-8d7c-9101291124da\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-aba08a56-ac3b-483c-be26-df69e0c3dd87\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f6b365d4-eea1-45e0-b434-20c34ec5ee3d\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>종이</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9a599582-69a8-4574-bc20-fed1f5036abf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a8fbf912-3f29-436d-b71e-47a151464626\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>일반지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0d614c9c-0eea-48f9-953d-7d9d3416dd82\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 아트지/스노우지/모조지 등</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-213bc664-e10a-4ba6-8b35-dcad04605753\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fef056ae-e774-47da-b02a-1ffef7e79dd5\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>고급지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5625448f-d020-41ee-846c-3fbfd6787245\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 랑데뷰/아르떼/반누브/머쉬지/슈퍼파일/인버코트지 등</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4b9cb35b-2e61-4866-a9bf-f02ec1cec4c5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4af62c08-6461-4b0a-a484-29f71aec4bae\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>색지</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-aaa37657-5241-40d7-8c44-5733f27c6d79\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 매직터치 계열 색지 (문의 요청)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-012df88f-1080-4f96-a12b-56feb6dd2ad9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2e6c6d80-bc1f-4c72-abd6-a79643dda6dc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>기타</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6d9bbb94-74de-4015-ad81-a83b37bcd491\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 물에 빠르게 녹는 MDP 종이 등이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-531f0278-9572-4bd1-8385-d4ff742a9e8c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ad54c7cc-6c85-445d-88e5-bc148a755ad0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-53a3738e-50c7-4b98-9ee3-e94b8397a120\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3ff65e62-a80d-4d34-be0c-3c704bcaf3fa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이는 일반적인 모든 종이로 제작이 가능합니다. 대량이 아닌 경우 디지털로 인쇄되기 때문에 디지털 전용지가 많이 포함되어 있습니다. 대량의 독판인 경우는 특별한 펄지나 기타 특수용지로도 제작이 가능합니다. 언제든 문의하십시오.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d08b6c84-221a-4e20-9884-8b6bcdcde000\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b6802f5d-093a-4241-8a41-847667a86b51\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d243b260-266c-41f3-8978-db32e3998312\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3540bf39-ec3f-41af-83d0-1efbf205cde4\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>사이즈</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e3b73c52-131f-40d1-bea1-0c5a5e9b4a47\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-caf32b41-9e6d-4f07-a902-f1af2b5f49eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>기본 사이즈</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-84c2686d-fea0-41ed-8b47-f5d2f091e739\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 약 80*700mm 이내</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ab73b88e-afdb-4994-a69b-ca8b9cb74ef3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8be9ca0d-e1a4-4888-b412-1900de14cce4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-561526f7-ecc6-4267-8054-d327c524475c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6b59d221-bd37-4d8d-9fdd-3850c4a5c36d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사이즈는 정말로 다양합니다. 띠지가 꼭 길어야 한다는 것도 아니고 고객님의 제품에 맞는 띠지가 가장 좋은 사이즈입니다. 물론 절수에 맞아야 합리적인 가격이 되겠으나 그것도 큰 의미 없습니다. 고객님의 제품에 가장 적합한 사이즈를 알려 주세요. 그러면 약간 수정해서 가장 합리적일 수 있는 사이즈를 제안 드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b884f977-69d1-4fac-829f-842d4a2fbd7e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-251c1036-bf51-4c76-8f22-35b9047e8038\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4dda1cdd-7f2b-496d-93f1-b232f7062caa\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-64bcbc76-8c26-4406-a7f8-5f5467da73f9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이 절수에 가장 딱 맞게 제작되는 사이즈가 가장 합리적인 단가를 공급받으실 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ab75c84d-4057-422c-96a8-8af898127a25\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-109b9871-5a0c-4d65-880f-1eb107faab60\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a33391cd-00ad-4545-b46e-ca366a61ef86\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-db14dd9d-7eb4-4d88-bfd0-22378c13fa1e\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-89faf69b-8fb0-499b-a0a0-2f6010b82f5c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-01e02e3b-1808-475f-9f4e-ede9e2d87c5f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>기본 인쇄</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-96fdcc29-bf33-4cd0-8c16-1970b403c328\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 단면 컬러 CMYK 4도 인쇄</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-26704d5f-d519-413f-9137-55caa2c0fc60\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4cf0d8c1-ca1e-40ec-a20b-f1adc4c778b1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">띠지는 단면 컬러 인쇄가 기본입니다. 다만 별색이나 실크 인쇄 등은 소량에서는 제작이 되지 않습니다. 대량 주문 시에는 모든 인쇄가 가능하므로 반드시 문의하시고 작업해 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-127bb6b3-a122-4763-ac23-fd2ff8bdb430\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2d3e4afe-5ba4-4f28-9425-c7db520135fa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0ee7430d-e04d-4d10-be0c-76439bececde\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e5989df8-d203-4cdb-af32-697566852a5f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">물론 띠지의 성격에 따라 양면인쇄도 하는 경우가 있습니다. 참고하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5e0bbf9c-36a3-431f-bab7-323aab73d96b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8eba2332-e1cf-44f4-8d89-dbc623926c27\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-59468977-f387-43af-acad-135890516377\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c6e90186-cfa1-40b4-9459-2bc761099ef4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">소량 디지털 인쇄에서는 별색인 특별한 경우 빼고는 제작이 불가능합니다. 물론 요즘은 별색을 출력하는 디지털 기계도 많이 나와 있지만 그 색상 또한 제한적입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-01c527d7-20ee-4187-991e-22c04ced7db5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-232af4d3-df6f-46e8-80e1-d9a055f17d4f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b67e72b8-4356-475a-af3f-8c36e6964bbf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b6ff7f21-2af0-42c1-b996-0e29cca927b0\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>후공정</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e760e1ca-4852-45fc-9ca8-65189060d174\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5889cf27-2d3e-47aa-8608-18a2cf40386c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>코팅</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5ba6fa91-1c17-4557-a617-b7c571934188\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 코팅 작업은 띠지 성격상 많이 하지는 않지만 제품을 보호하는 트레이(Tray)용으로 띠지를 제작할 경우 코팅으로 더 단단하게 고정하도록 코팅을 많이 합니다. 코팅은 유광/무광/부분코팅 등이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0459e601-422b-499e-b72f-79bf5ce7ff8f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223965416452/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8528bcb3-6e53-4660-ab11-869c32161a92\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-83aafdc2-2dc8-4135-99c0-d6231525a54a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-db10a52f-e44f-4912-84a8-87f5301064c2\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2a5ba0ed-432b-46bc-91b2-31d420b34a36\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-81f3a744-e3eb-4e4f-bbb5-68a6f85fff5f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>오시(누름선)</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8361f63c-7204-4fdb-93ab-ebf1e8ed4523\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 띠지는 용도에 따라 오시선을 넣어 잘 접히도록 제작합니다. 이는 오시를 넣지 않고 제품을 감싸는 용으로도 제작되기도 하지만 오시를 넣어서 접히는 중간중간 잘 접히도록 만들 수도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e21620ba-27cb-4d8c-857e-ec304130ab4d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1898ab34-e7c6-4673-a28a-ef5df232f642\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-408b64dc-ce4e-4429-a34c-783648af97e4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8f4b1b0e-4349-4adf-acc7-53509c83ed67\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 후공정은 제품의 용도와 밀접한 관계가 있습니다. 상의하시고 선택하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5f9b3611-8549-440b-a6e6-29547994b324\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3b2ead43-e9ec-41db-a169-00afd2b0a69e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e82e963a-ead6-4bf7-9a3e-43153e9d34ab\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-f0b01dd3-d519-48ea-88bd-efb4563d3117\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>접착</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-831c79c4-b1c0-4a73-bef2-9aa0e2798de7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 띠지인 만큼 접착을 해서 제품을 감싸도록 만들 수 있습니다. 물론 접착을 하지 않고 다른 방법으로도 제작되기도 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ce18d3f1-4bc0-45dc-bf36-d5d279c984be\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a6530aa1-dc58-4292-8ec2-0df65d080b41\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bbd27226-b3fb-4235-b9cf-0fabfc2c4adc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-9c3f3955-3d43-4957-b08b-2c3e73a0bbf0\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>수량</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7062710a-fdcb-4c75-b8b0-184a0653dd66\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b515624f-f605-4cde-949b-d4135739f802\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>기본 수량</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f32f50dc-dc54-4e64-8eac-13dcbf034aca\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 단 한 장에서부터 제작 가능</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8743c4e7-dfe9-408c-9d54-f251b2ad3421\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cc82f4a4-debc-4338-883e-7b99dfd41107\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디지털 인쇄가 기본이 되면서 단 한 장으로 제작이 가능합니다. 하지만 한 장의 가격이 싸지 않을 수 있기 때문에 가장 합리적인 수량으로 제작해야 합니다. 디지털의 경우는 큰 차이가 안날 수 있지만 대량 오프셋 인쇄 방식의 경우는 사이즈를 잘 판단해서 주문하셔야 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4bcd70eb-bde4-486a-8a98-4022b37120cf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e46e5baf-aa56-4de1-bda0-fb389e85d045\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fa218c8e-af18-4456-b606-7dcfc598de7c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e74b72b4-d086-4928-a777-02b264018b5f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">대량으로 제작하신다면 반드시 상담을 통해 수량을 파악하고 주문하십시오. 사이즈에 따라 수량이 많이 차이 나고 가격의 편차가 큽니다. 전화 주세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-53910440-e932-4d17-80ef-bd87a85f4fb8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-fd9f7479-76e2-4851-82e8-4c5b34e14577\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-113f6e27-0f68-430d-8be6-1d9e7e16e5eb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-e339a8bf-c5e0-46ff-9d01-07ffba062fe2\" style=\"\">이런 고객님은 문의하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ad9d2ba7-8563-4aae-86db-24d32622fb94\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-e38c222e-6fce-4bec-870e-f0a09f35f0e0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-113ffe00-ce38-4f70-9b27-7d143ff4e463\" style=\"color:#555555;\">□ 제품을 감싸는 띠지에 추석 이미지를 넣고 싶으신 분</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-1ebafdc0-17b1-4176-819b-c3ef68a5fb91\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-dca65971-9982-4681-99ab-9b0214de62cb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">□ 띠지를 제작해 보고 싶은데 어떻게 하는 방법이나 사양이 어려우신 분</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-5b1a4ca2-d475-4bd2-ab5e-8b0e4a05eec9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-58461b8f-dbff-4c1e-9cfa-fc3117e1f840\" style=\"color:#555555;\">□ 제품 포장에 관심이 많은 신규 스타트업 제품 판매회사</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-e032be6a-560e-4caa-8925-a33618547757\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223965416452/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-17d3abfe-a015-4272-aaa7-c23688467717\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-16e26130-ae07-455a-b356-d668d8372d19\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-df14399f-57b9-4937-8e45-ea1e0ef64f55\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니의 주요 고객은 신규 제품을 런칭하시는 스타트업 회사가 많습니다.</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0d43cdc9-9398-4b9b-a6d4-721abb1e7e45\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 이유는 친절한 상담 때문이 아닌가 합니다. 처음 런칭하시고 인쇄를 잘 모르실 때 (주)파파스컴퍼니은 친절한 상담을 통해 거애 유무를 떠나 상담해 드리고 있습니다. 물론 모든 고객님께 100% 정확한 응대를 하지 않지만 앞으로도 이 상담 인력만큼은 더 디테일하고 정확한 안내를 통해 고객님께 도움을 드리고자 노력하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-30f20c41-8b59-4098-8d24-90cf48e49845\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-726cdaa1-6560-49ca-9b6a-587672eeca51\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-3541b455-9d55-4e7a-bdd3-b6ca1bcb5e21\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-75b6feac-3d69-4f39-b7b9-0740602fb5bf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">언제든 궁금한 사항은 편하게 문의하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7bd6f169-550c-46d8-a51a-c09e37c1559b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223965416452/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-364dcdda-6c07-42aa-a5f7-3f3628914ba6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223965416452/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-79eba2a2-27d6-46f0-a2d7-3e8b209e30d5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-31c83cab-ab04-4137-b68b-cc42c03862b8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-24ae41f1-f8fb-4147-9278-5edd398743cb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
}